raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: Babe? 
Player: Are you home? 👀
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\")
	do echo_set([\"127\"])
	Mabel: Uhm... 
	Mabel: No...? 🙈
	Player: Okay
	do echo_clear()
	do advance_time(0, 52)
	Mabel: Sorry babe, I was home
	Mabel: I'm just sooo embarassed 🙃
	Player: Of what?
	Mabel: It's embarassing 😶
	Mabel: You sure you want to hear it?
	Player: Of course I do
	Mabel: Well... okay
	Mabel: I had a weird dream 🙃
	Player: What kind of dream?
	Mabel: You were in my room and we were both squished on my bed 🙈
	Player: We've done that before a few times 😆
	Mabel: Yeah but uhh..
	Mabel: It got a little warm so I might have taken off something and you might have gotten curious about it so I let you touch me and feel a little but it was really sensitive and then I made a weird sound and that's when I noticed your messages
	Mabel: 🙈
	Player: Whoa 😆
	Player: That's an explanation I guess
	Mabel: I had a few dreams like this
	Mabel: And they're getting a little more vivid 😳
	Mabel: Babe do I have a fever?? 😭
	- Definitely some kind of fever 😌
		Player: Definitely some kind of fever 😌
		Mabel: Omg am I really sick 🥲
		Player: Not the sick kind haha
	- You're fine!
		Player: You're fine!
		Mabel: If you think so 🥲
	Mabel: What are you doing on tomorrow night by the way? 👉👈
	Player: Hmm, nothing I think
	Mabel: Do you wanna maybe come over?
	Player: Sure, what time
	Mabel: Like at 8?
	Player: Pm? That's barely enough time 😅 since I need to catch the bus to go back home
	Mabel: Well I mean, you could stay if you want.. for the night
	Mabel: Thought: All the other girls on my floor have their boys over..
	Player: Like at your dorm?
	Mabel: Thought: It's time to be extra cute!
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Mhmm..
	Mabel: img: mabel/128
	Player: Oh, sure. That sounds nice 😊
	Mabel: Yay! 🥳
	Mabel: I have a lot of preparing to do then 💃
	- Buying some sexy PJs?
		set Story.flag = \"LingerieRequest\"
		Player: Buying some sexy PJs?
